 1998-19711998-11-030,  INDUSTRY,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of the following persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (CINDY SPRAGUE, of Ottawa, Ontario, in the place of Rita De Santis, whose term has expired; and V. JENNY COCO, of Windsor, Ontario, in the place of Doreen Braverman, whose term has expired)
